KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS: PLAINTEXT://localhost:9092

Kafka works locally
but services fromother container can't connect ❌, becasue it only work for lochalhost inside kafka container
so change it to

KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS: PLAINTEXT://broker:9092
why broker? becasue it's the name of the container, if container name is kafk, change it to kafka
so we connect to this container service using it's own name, it's like domain name, we dont use ip of this container